```py
def consecutive_letters(string):
    for i in range(len(string) - 1):
        if string[i] == string[i + 1]:
            return True
    return False
```

```py
def consecutive_letters(string):
    window = string[:2]
    for letter in string[2:]:
        if window[0] == window[1]:
            return True
        window = window[1] + letter
    return window[0] == window[1]
```
